Title: NuMvvm
Description: NuMvvm is a lightweight MVVM library.
HomeWiki:
NuMvvm is a lightweight MVVM library.

The library consists of:
  • ViewModelBase (provides property change notification and validation)
  • RelayCommand implementation.
